Banyan Mouse Brain

Carter Allen

11/8/2021

Load Packages

library(SeuratData)
library(Seurat)
library(banyan)
library(patchwork)

Install Data

# InstallData("stxBrain")
brain <- LoadData("stxBrain","anterior1")

Pre-Processing

# run Seurat processing steps
brain <- SCTransform(brain, assay = "Spatial", verbose = FALSE)
brain <- RunPCA(brain, assay = "SCT", verbose = FALSE)

Fit Model

# fit banyan model
brain_fit <- fit_banyan(seurat_obj = brain, K = 6)
# plot labels
plot_labels(brain_fit)

Get Continuous Scores

# calculate scores
brain_fit <- get_scores(brain_fit)
str(brain_fit)

# plot uncertainty
plot_uncertainty(brain_fit)

# plot propensity
plot_propensity(brain_fit,k = 1) + plot_propensity(brain_fit,k = 2)

Plot Community Structure

# plot connectivity matrix
plot_connectivity_matrix(brain_fit)

# plot connectivity interval
plot_connectivity_intervals(brain_fit)

Plot Adjacency Matrices

# plot adjacency matrix - expression
a1_plot <- plot_adjacency_matrix(brain_fit,
                      layer = "expression")

# plot adjacency matrix - spatial
a2_plot <- plot_adjacency_matrix(brain_fit,
                      layer = "spatial")
